    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="bol_ch.00003_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey U S America</name>
                    <date when="1885-08-03" rend="right">Aug: 3d '85<ptr target="bol.00002_n2"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Bessie and Isabella Ford</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I will at least write a line to say I have safely received your and Edward
                Carpenter's affectionate generous gift of &#163;50.<ptr target="bol.00002_n1"/> It has come very opportunely
                &#38; I thank you all&#8212;I have been prostrated lately by sun-stroke, but am well recovering from
                it&#8212;</p>
            
            <closer>
                <salute>God bless you, dear friends,</salute>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
